name: Axis Auto Finance Inc.
longDescription: Axis Auto Finance Inc is a fintech company that is changing the way used vehicles are purchased and financed in Canada. The company's direct-to-consumer website, DriveAxis.ca, enables users to choose their next used vehicle, customize financing terms, and get the car delivered to homes. In addition, the company continues to grow business to business non-prime auto loan originations by delivering innovative technology solutions and superior service to its dealer partners.
